  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><ul><li>Oversea Shipment and logistics</li><li>Increasing our Company's market share</li><li>Business development / Sales.</li><li>Suppliers sourcing and liaison</li><li>Purchases and price negotiation.</li><li>Increase of Product range revenue yearly</li><li>Reporting to the Director/Manager of the Company</li><li>Others as assigned</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties if necessary</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>‘A’ Level, Diploma in related discipline or equivalent</li><li>Be resourceful, problem-solving, meticulous, organized and close attention to details</li><li>No experiences needed</li><li>Good knowledge & familiar in MS Office such as Words & Excel is a must</li><li>Knowledge of Japanese language is a Plus</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
